flowchart TD
    START([New Request]) --> INIT[starter-init<br/>Bootstrap harness]
    INIT --> AMBIG{Behavior<br/>understood?}

    AMBIG -- No --> RES[spec-research<br/>Investigate / brownfield map]
    RES --> SPEC[spec-requirements<br/>Grilling waves + spec.md]
    AMBIG -- Yes --> SPEC

    SPEC --> VIS[visualize<br/>Diagrams when useful]
    SPEC -. architecture decision .-> ADR[spec-adr<br/>Record decision]
    VIS --> PLAN[spec-plan<br/>design.md + tasks.md]
    ADR --> PLAN

    PLAN --> IMPL[spec-implement<br/>One task at a time]
    IMPL --> VER[harness-verify<br/>Gate + alignment + security]

    VER -- Gate fail --> IMPL
    VER -- Drift --> SPEC
    VER -- Pass --> SYNC[Post-Ship Sync<br/>context-memory sweep]
    SYNC --> ENDS[context-session END<br/>handoff + extracts]
    ENDS --> DONE([Done])

    VER -. harness lesson .-> HARN[harness<br/>Improve Mode]
    HARN -. durable fix .-> INIT

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef primary fill:#fff,stroke:#10a37f,color:#0d0d0d,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef neutral fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d,stroke-width:1.2px
    classDef loop fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d

    class START,DONE terminal
    class SPEC,PLAN,SYNC primary
    class INIT,RES,VIS,ADR,IMPL,VER,ENDS,HARN neutral
    class AMBIG loop
